                "name": "Volley",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A Glorious Reclamation sergeant troop can fire a volley of arrows as a standard action. This attack takes the form of up to four lines with a range of 100 feet. These lines can start from the corner of any square in the troop\u2019s space. All creatures in any of these lines take 5d6 points of piercing damage (Reflex DC 21 half). The save DC is Dexterity-based."
